cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with facial recognition and analysis using 3D scanning devices, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of deep convolutional neural networks (CNN) and geometric deep learning techniques also suggests the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The adaptation of meshes for the use of deep CNNs falls under the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category, while the use of models trained on 3D range scans suggests the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
